/home/maysarah/TechTest.serviceRawFile:
service: my-laravel-service

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: provided.al2
  region: us-east-1
  memorySize: 512
  timeout: 60
  environment:
    APP_ENV: production
    APP_DEBUG: false
    APP_KEY: ${env:APP_KEY}
    DB_CONNECTION: mysql
    DB_HOST: ${env:DB_HOST}
    DB_PORT: 3306
    DB_DATABASE: ${env:DB_DATABASE}
    DB_USERNAME: ${env:DB_USERNAME}
    DB_PASSWORD: ${env:DB_PASSWORD}

plugins:
  - ./vendor/bref/bref

functions:
  web:
    handler: public/index.php
    layers:
      - ${bref:layer.php-82-fpm}  # PHP 8.2 layer
    events:
      - httpApi: '*'  # Expose this Lambda function as an HTTP API
